snippet.title: Pinnacle Point - Gameplay Teaser (Trailer)
snippet.description:
Wishlist here: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2875410/Pinnacle_Point/

A lot has been happening behind the scenes, and I wanted to take a moment to say thanks. The support, feedback, and excitement for Pinnacle Point have been incredible, and I've been hard at work making sure the demo delivers.

If everything goes as planned, the DEMO should be out around April or early May. I'll have more details soon, but one thing's for sure—the island won't stay quiet forever.

For streamers and content creators: I'll be sending out early access keys for the demo ahead of launch. If you want to be first in line, email me at cagedelephant666@gmail.com to get on the waiting list.
